ste\u00e5rsstudentene prioriteres p\u00e5 ventelistene i denne perioden."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "student"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "a9f25ce50e0bad6cedbc87470fcfe43c937fe0904fcb06ffece09fa4fa24cef6"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2013-04-15T08:07:19.865Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "De siste to m\u00e5nedene har Studentsamskipnaden i Trondheim f\u00e5tt over 3000 s\u00f8knader."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1361909.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Berg%20studentby"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/04338f963ae2b3e34bd7d87a20fb36b732fc7a65.jpg?59877f94"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Sit drukner i s\u00f8knader fra studenter -adressa.no", "Deler ut kontrakter i mai", "- V\u00e6r tidlig ute", "Lange ventelister p\u00e5 Berg studentby"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "04338f963ae2b3e34bd7d87a20fb36b732fc7a65"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim", "ukeadressa", "eadressa", "skattelister", "d\u00f8dsfall", "tr\u00f8nder", "trafikk"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "nyheter,trondheim,ukeadressa,eadressa,skattelister,d\u00f8dsfall,tr\u00f8nder,trafikk"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "student"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["bolig", "studentby", "student", "studere", "tidlig ute", "s\u00f8knader", "hybel", "trondheim", "venteliste"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["samordna", "lerkendal", "steinan", "studentsamskipnaden", "moholt", "sit"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["berg", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "cathrine kristiansen"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "student"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1361909